      "comment": "TOP BIN NISMO (6) stalked the lead from the inside draw then took over turning and burst clear to score (22.49) at this track in a Maiden over 400m. Well placed and can measure up. GRAND FORTE (1) stalked the lead from a low draw then burst clear to score (22.93) at The Gardens in a Grade 5 over 400m. One of the key runners again. ARMATREE FREDDO (2) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (23.00) at Gosford. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Leading chance. BOMBAY (8) is another with top-three prospects.",
